# Digital Wallet System Backend (Flask)

This project is a digital wallet backend system built with Flask and MongoDB.

## Features

- User Registration & Login (JWT)
- Deposit, Withdraw, and Transfer Funds
- Fraud Detection
- Admin Dashboard

## Setup

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Add a `.env` file with:
```
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/wallet
JWT_SECRET_KEY=your_jwt_secret
```

Run:
```bash
python app.py
```

## API Endpoints

- POST /api/auth/register
- POST /api/auth/login
- POST /api/wallet/deposit
- POST /api/wallet/withdraw
- POST /api/wallet/transfer
- GET /api/admin/flagged
- GET /api/admin/top-users
- GET /api/admin/total-balance
